snippet.title: Marvel's Avengers: Kate Bishop - Taking AIM Trailer
snippet.description:
Kate Bishop resurfaces to investigate Nick Fury's disappearance, but ends up uncovering AIM's new plan. In order to unravel the mystery, she enlists the help of the Avengers. Available December 8!
